  "detailed_description": "Become a Knight as save a village from a goblin invasion.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173620/extras/Description_Shot_1.PNG?t=1725834987\" /></span><br>Fight through intricate puzzles and defeat all goblins to advance to the next stage.<br>Push around objects such as rocks, boxes, and many more to make way or use them to crush goblins.<br>Or strike the goblins yourself with upmost justice.<br>Each stage offers increasing difficulty to test your mettle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173620/extras/Description_Shot_2.PNG?t=1725834987\" /></span><br>Face against giant goblin bosses with their unique gimmick and prove your might.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173620/extras/Description_Shot_3.PNG?t=1725834987\" /></span><br>Uncover a grander story accompanied by anime arts.<br>Find out the true nature of the Knights, are they the beacon of hope or something worse waiting to happen?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173620/extras/Description_Shot_4.PNG?t=1725834987\" /></span><br>Bring the fight to the evil force.<br>From the village then straight to their nest.<br>Leave none of them alive!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173620/extras/Description_Shot_5.PNG?t=1725834987\" /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Become a Knight as save a village from a goblin invasion.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173620/extras/Description_Shot_1.PNG?t=1725834987\" /></span><br>Fight through intricate puzzles and defeat all goblins to advance to the next stage.<br>Push around objects such as rocks, boxes, and many more to make way or use them to crush goblins.<br>Or strike the goblins yourself with upmost justice.<br>Each stage offers increasing difficulty to test your mettle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173620/extras/Description_Shot_2.PNG?t=1725834987\" /></span><br>Face against giant goblin bosses with their unique gimmick and prove your might.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173620/extras/Description_Shot_3.PNG?t=1725834987\" /></span><br>Uncover a grander story accompanied by anime arts.<br>Find out the true nature of the Knights, are they the beacon of hope or something worse waiting to happen?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173620/extras/Description_Shot_4.PNG?t=1725834987\" /></span><br>Bring the fight to the evil force.<br>From the village then straight to their nest.<br>Leave none of them alive!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173620/extras/Description_Shot_5.PNG?t=1725834987\" /></span>",
